{"questionId":"22229610","questionHtml":"<p>Calculate the height of the tree <math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\"><mn>6</mn></math> years from now. Give your answer correct to the nearest <math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\"><mi>cm</mi></math>.</p>","markschemeHtml":"<p>recognizing geometric sequence, <math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\"><mi>r</mi><mo>=</mo><mn>0</mn><mo>.</mo><mn>8</mn><mo>&nbsp;</mo></math>&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; <em><strong>(M1)</strong></em></p>\n<p>attempt to find total height by adding initial height to a term in series&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; <em><strong>(M1)</strong></em></p>\n<p><strong>EITHER</strong></p>\n<p><strong><math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\"><mn>42</mn><mo>+</mo><mfrac><mrow><mn>4</mn><mfenced><mrow><mn>1</mn><mo>-</mo><msup><mfenced><mrow><mn>0</mn><mo>.</mo><mn>8</mn></mrow></mfenced><mn>6</mn></msup></mrow></mfenced></mrow><mrow><mn>1</mn><mo>-</mo><mfenced><mrow><mn>0</mn><mo>.</mo><mn>8</mn></mrow></mfenced></mrow></mfrac></math>&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; <em>(A1)</em></strong></p>\n<p><strong>OR</strong></p>\n<p><strong><math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\"><mn>37</mn><mo>+</mo><mfrac><mrow><mn>5</mn><mfenced><mrow><mn>1</mn><mo>-</mo><msup><mfenced><mrow><mn>0</mn><mo>.</mo><mn>8</mn></mrow></mfenced><mn>7</mn></msup></mrow></mfenced></mrow><mrow><mn>1</mn><mo>-</mo><mfenced><mrow><mn>0</mn><mo>.</mo><mn>8</mn></mrow></mfenced></mrow></mfrac></math>&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; <em>(A1)</em></strong></p>\n<p><strong>THEN</strong></p>\n<p><math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\"><mo>=</mo><mn>56</mn><mo>.</mo><mn>7571</mn><mo>…</mo></math></p>\n<p><math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\"><mo>=</mo><mn>56</mn><mo>.</mo><mn>76</mn><mo> </mo><mfenced><mi mathvariant=\"normal\">m</mi></mfenced></math> <strong>OR</strong> <math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\"><mn>5676</mn><mo> </mo><mfenced><m